<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Back in 2020 and 2021, as pharmaceutical compa=
nies were racing to develop and distribute a Covid-19 vaccine, I <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL25ld3NsZXR0ZXJzLzIwMjAtMDctMjMvbW9uZXktc3R1ZmY=
teW91LWRvbi10LW5lZWQtcHJvZml0cy1hbnltb3JlP2NtcGlkPUJCRDEwMDkyM19NT05FWVNUVU=
ZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTAwO=
SZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2c876945" itempr=
op=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: =
#000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border=
-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;=
"> wrote</a> a few <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click=
/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLz=
IwMjEtMDItMjQvdGhlLXZhY2NpbmUtaXMtbm90LWEtY29tcGV0aXRpb24_Y21waWQ9QkJEMTAwO=
TIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRt=
X3Rlcm09MjMxMDA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa=
07fa8c3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> times</a> about the vaccine and index funds. The idea was=
:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">A global pandemic is bad for business=
: People are locked down, no one is going to restaurants or flying on plane=
s, lots of companies are losing money.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5=
px;">A broadly available vaccine would be good for business: Cruise-ship co=
mpanies and airlines and mall owners and every other company would benefit =
if a vaccine was developed quickly and distributed widely.</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Most US publicly traded companies =E2=80=94=C2=A0p=
harmaceutical companies and cruise-ship companies and mall owners and every=
one else =E2=80=94=C2=A0are owned in large part by the same group of big as=
set managers, index funds and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2F=
ydGljbGVzLzIwMTctMDItMDkvcXVhc2ktaW5kZXhlcnMtZ3Jvd3RoLWFuZC1jb25mdXNpb24_Y2=
1waWQ9QkJEMTAwOTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld=
3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMxMDA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4=
b8524a319a23cB442dd291" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;"> quasi-indexers</a> and other diversified i=
nvestors.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Therefore, the universal=
 owners of the stock market should be calling up the pharma companies and s=
aying things like=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cpool your knowledge to make a vaccine fast,=
 and don=E2=80=99t worry about who gets the credit,=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Co=
nce you have a vaccine, throw everything at mass producing it and then dist=
ribute it cheap to everyone.=E2=80=9D This might cost the pharma companies =
a lot of money, but it would be good for=C2=A0<em>their owners</em>, the un=
iversal shareholders, so they should do it. They should sacrifice their pro=
fits for the broader profits of the business world, not out of selflessness=
 but because=C2=A0<em>they work for their owners, who own the whole busines=
s world</em>.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You could object to various bits of this, and =
I am not sure it was a practical guide to the behavior of pharmaceutical co=
mpanies or big asset managers or even Covid lockdowns.=C2=A0 But in broad s=
trokes, the pharma companies were creating drug that would=C2=A0<em>vastly =
increase=C2=A0consumption in general</em>, a universal stimulant for econom=
ic demand.=C2=A0You got a shot, and then you went out and took plane trips =
and cruises and ate at restaurants and went to a WeWork. All sorts of busin=
esses should want to encourage a drug that increases general consumption.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And the universal ownership mechanism, in theo=
ry, created=C2=A0a new way to do that. Instead of the usual model of corpor=
ate capitalism =E2=80=94=C2=A0companies competing against each other, motiv=
ated by prices and profits =E2=80=94=C2=A0there is <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZX=
JnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTYtMDgtMjQvYXJlLWluZGV4LWZ1bmRzLWNvbW11b=
mlzdD9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMDA5MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3Vy=
Y2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzEwMDkmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607=
f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB860ea0f3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemsco=
pe" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !impor=
tant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom=
-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> a new model</a>, in which the comp=
anies all work for the same owners and are, in some very loose theoretical =
sense, all divisions of the same universal trust. This might make it easier=
 for companies to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzI=
wMjAtMDItMjEvdGhlLWNvbXBhbmllcy1hcmUtb24tdGhlLXNhbWUtdGVhbT9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMD=
A5MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1d=
G1fdGVybT0yMzEwMDkmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23c=
Bc9fa1ab4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank"=
 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;"> coordinate with each other</a>, to sacrifice any one co=
mpany=E2=80=99s profits to make all of the companies better off. This might=
 be good (companies won=E2=80=99t selfishly pollute if the pollution makes =
things worse for other companies), or it might be bad (companies <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjAtMDItMjEvdGhlLWNvbXBhbml=
lcy1hcmUtb24tdGhlLXNhbWUtdGVhbT9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMDA5MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbW=
VkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzEwMDkmdXRtX2Nhb=
XBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cCc9fa1ab4" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> might no=
t compete on price</a>). The point is just that universal ownership of the =
stock market should mean that companies are more likely to do what is good =
for companies in general, and less likely to do what is good only for one p=
articular company.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And universal ownership of the stock market in=
tersected with the development of a product, the Covid vaccine, that was al=
most universally good for business.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#foo=
tnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-=
bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none =
!important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block=
;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But imagine a pharmaceutical company that has =
invented a different drug, an opposite drug, a drug=C2=A0that=C2=A0<em>redu=
ces consumption in general</em>, a universal demand suppressant. It makes t=
he people who take it so much happier and more fulfilled that they=C2=A0<em=
>don=E2=80=99t want anything else</em>. They eat less food and drink less a=
lcohol and buy fewer clothes and take fewer vacations and get fewer haircut=
s and consume less social media and click on fewer online ads and otherwise=
 consume much less.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you were the chief executive officer of a p=
ublicly traded pharmaceutical company and your researchers invented that dr=
ug, what would you think? On the one hand, you could probably sell it for a=
 lot of money and have big profits.=C2=A0On the other hand, it=E2=80=99s go=
ing to be really bad for all the other companies, the ones selling food and=
 alcohol and vacations and online ads. And the shareholders who own your co=
mpany also own those companies. Probably more of them. Your profits come at=
 the expense of the rest of your owners=E2=80=99 portfolio. By making money=
 for them in your business, you are making them worse off overall.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you started rolling out this drug, might Bl=
ackRock call you up to say =E2=80=9Cbuddy you gotta nix this one, it=E2=80=
=99s killing all our other businesses=E2=80=9D? No. No. BlackRock doesn=E2=
=80=99t work that way. This is all a tongue-in-cheek hypothetical about how=
 the stock market abstractly might work, not how it actually works. Plus th=
is drug is fictional.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Ozempic is not fictional, and while it is =
not exactly a universal demand suppressant=C2=A0it does suppress a lot of d=
emand. Bloomberg=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMjMtMTAtMDcvb3plbXBpYy1mb3Itd2VpZ2h0LWxvc3MtaXMtZGlzcnVwdGluZy1jb21wY=
W5pZXMtYnVzaW5lc3MtbW9kZWw_Y21waWQ9QkJEMTAwOTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1=
bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMxMDA5JnV0bV9jYW1wYWl=
nbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB799b10a2" itemprop=3D"StoryLink"=
 itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-de=
coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Leslie Patton=
