<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do hope that some universal owners are doing=
 the math. As a rough cut,=C2=A024 million Ozempic prescriptions at <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6L=
