ed down, though; also surely some=C2=A0of it will be paid for by insurance =
companies (also owned by universal shareholders!).</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile the average Ozempic user probably is=
n=E2=80=99t cutting her budget for groceries, cigarettes, alcohol, Instagra=
m, etc. by $1,000 a month? I would guess?=C2=A0Maybe it is a positive? I do=
