 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> squandered it</a> on=
 dumb crypto trades and endorsement deals.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But this story is not exactly right. There was=
 not money sitting in customer accounts that was then transferred to Alamed=
a accounts and squandered. FTX was a futures exchange; it <a href=3D"https:=
