 interest payment</a> on the debt that Musk took out to buy Twitter?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But he saved that $143 million by breaking the=
 law:=C2=A0The rules quite clearly required him to disclose his stake by Ma=
rch 24, and he did not. And in fact the SEC recently <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32969259.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdv=
