t sure there is=C2=A0<em>much=C2=A0</em>to be gained by asking him =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0the rule is pretty black-and-white, not based on intent, and the o=
bjective facts that he has publicly admitted to confirm that he violated it=
 =E2=80=94=C2=A0but I suppose if he had a good explanation for what happene=
